<doc>
  <member name="ID3D10RasterizerState.GetDesc">
    <summary>
      <para>Get the properties of a rasterizer-state object.</para>
    </summary>
    <param name="pDesc">
      <para>Type: <b><see cref="D3D10_RASTERIZER_DESC" />*</b></para>
      <para>Pointer to a rasterizer-state description (see <see cref="D3D10_RASTERIZER_DESC" />).</para>
    </param>
    <seealso cref="ID3D10RasterizerState Interface" />
  </member>
  <member name="ID3D10RasterizerState">
    <summary>
      <para>A rasterizer-state interface accesses rasterizer state for the <a href="https://docs.microsoft.com//windows/desktop/direct3d11/d3d10-graphics-programming-guide-rasterizer-stage">rasterizer stage</a>.</para>
    </summary>
    <remarks>
      <para>A rasterizer-state object is created with <see cref="ID3D10Device.CreateRasterizerState" /> and bound to the pipeline with <see cref="ID3D10Device.RSSetState" />.</para>
    </remarks>
    <seealso href="https://docs.microsoft.com//windows/desktop/direct3d10/d3d10-graphics-reference-d3d10-core-interfaces">Core Interfaces</seealso>
    <seealso cref="ID3D10DeviceChild" />
  </member>
</doc>